What you need to know:

Simba's only loss in the competition was against Al Ahly last Friday as they amassed 13 points, two above Al AhlyThe 21-time Tanzanian Premier League champions will know their opponents in the quarter-final stage when Caf holds the draw on April 30Apart from Onyango, another Kenyan international Brian Mandela will also feature in the quarter-final stage after his team Mamelodi Sundowns of South Africa made the cut